# Responsive Standards

Mobile First.

Breakpoints:

Mobile:
320px–767px

Tablet:
768px–1024px

Desktop:
1025px+

## Requirements

No horizontal scroll.

No clipped content.

No overlapping text.

No overflowing containers.

## Typography

Use clamp().

Examples:

Hero:
clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem)

Heading:
clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem)

Body:
clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem)

## Layout

Editorial grids on desktop.

Elegant stacking on mobile.
